c_{1}^{\prime}\rightarrow c_{1}^{\prime\prime}=\frac{c_{1}^{\prime}}{\left|c_{1}^{\prime}\right|}\sqrt{\left|c_{1}^{\prime}\right|^{2}+d\rho}
